B.a0f=new A.j("im_17",B.t,"Entwined leg-lock grind: Legs cross and lock around waists like living ropes \u2014 thighs clamping hips, calves hooked behind backs. Torsos pull flush: chests flatten completely, stomachs seal, ribs rising together with each inhale. Arms encircle tightly; fingers dig into shoulder blades for leverage. Circles are tight and deep: hips grinding in small, insistent orbits that send pressure radiating up spines and down locked thighs. Muscles tense and release in waves \u2014 a subtle tremor traveling the full length of entwined limbs. Heat builds in the core first, then spreads outward; sweat slicks the pressed skin, turning every shift into a smooth, gliding friction. Breaths shorten, mingling in the hot space between faces, hearts pounding in near-perfect sync through the locked connection.","assets/images/pos_im17.png","Entwined leg-lock grind: Legs waists ke charo taraf living ropes ki tarah lock ho jayenge \u2014 thighs hips ko clamp karengi, calves backs ke peeche hook honge. Torsos flush honge: chests puri tarah flat, stomachs seal, har saas ke saath ribs saath mein uthenge. Arms tightly encircle; ungliyan shoulder blades mein dig karengi leverage ke liye. Circles tight aur deep hain: hips small insistent orbits mein grind karenge jo spines aur thighs mein pressure bhejenge. Muscles tensed aur release honge waves mein. Heat core mein build hogi aur bahar phail jayegi; sweat skin ko slick karega, har shift ko ek smooth gliding friction mein badal dega.")
B.a1a=new A.j("im_18",B.t,"Side-by-side full merge: Lying on sides facing each other: one leg slides between mine, the other hooks outside, interlocking like interlocking gears. Chests press flat first \u2014 nipples brushing, then flattening with weight. Stomachs mold; hips nestle tightly. The merge is total: from shoulders to ankles, bodies form one continuous plane. Figure-eight grinds begin at the hips \u2014 slow loops that ripple upward through torsos (ribs expanding together) and downward through legs (thighs flexing in sequence). Warmth pools where pubic bones meet, spreading like slow-moving honey; sweat gathers in the creases of bent knees and elbows. The motion creates a continuous, flowing friction \u2014 skin gliding with faint, wet whispers, breaths fanning cheeks in warm pulses.","assets/images/pos_im18.png","Side-by-side full merge: Sides par let jao face-to-face: ek leg mere legs ke beech slide hogi, dusri bahar, interlocking gears ki tarah. Chests flat press honge \u2014 nipples brushing, phir weight ke saath flat. Stomachs mold; hips nestle tightly. Merge total hai: shoulders se ankles tak, bodies ek continuous plane banayengi. Figure-eight grinds hips se shuru honge \u2014 slow loops jo torsos aur legs mein ripple karenge. Warmth pubic bones par pool karegi aur slow-moving honey ki tarah phail jayegi. Sweat knee aur elbows ke creases mein jama hoga. Motion continuous friction banayega \u2014 skin wet whispers ke saath glide karegi.")
B.a1b=new A.j("im_19",B.t,"Standing wrap-and-lift grind: One leg wraps high around my waist (or both if balance allows); I support your thigh with one hand, the other at your lower back. Hips align and lock \u2014 pubic bones pressing with firm, grounding force. Chests flatten; stomachs seal; shoulders touch. The grind is controlled and deep: upward lift drags your torso along mine in a long, warm slide, nipples tracing paths of fire; downward sink adds delicious weight and pressure. Gravity pulls bodies tighter; sweat forms in the small of your back and along my chest, making every roll slicker. Breaths turn hot and short against necks; the faint creak of shifting weight and soft exhales fill the space between.","assets/images/pos_im19.png","Standing wrap-and-lift grind: Ek leg meri waist ke charo taraf (ya dono agar balance ho sake); main ek hath se thigh support karunga aur dusra lower back par. Hips align aur lock honge \u2014 pubic bones firm pressure ke saath press honge. Chests flat; stomachs seal; shoulders touch. Grind controlled aur deep hai: upward lift tumhari torso ko meri torso par lamba slide karega, nipples aag ki tarah trace karenge; downward sink delicious weight aur pressure add karega. Gravity bodies ko aur tight kheenchegi; sweat back aur chest par banega, har roll ko slicker banayega. Saansein hot aur short ho jayengi.")
B.Zn=new A.j("im_20",B.t,"Slow full-body wave: Any aligned position \u2014 face-to-face or spooned. The wave starts at the crown: shoulders roll forward first, creating a gentle compression that flows downward \u2014 chest pressing harder, stomach sliding, hips lifting slightly, thighs tensing, calves flexing, toes curling. Then the wave reverses: toes uncurl first, calves relax, thighs soften, hips settle, stomach releases, chest eases, shoulders drop. Each full pass feels like liquid heat traveling the length of the body chain \u2014 skin warming in sequence, subtle tremors following the motion like aftershocks. Sweat gathers along the contact line, turning the wave into a smooth, gliding current. Breaths deepen to match the rhythm; hearts beat in slow, heavy sync; the entire connection hums with living warmth until every inch feels alive and electric.","assets/images/pos_im20.png","Slow full-body wave: Kisi bhi aligned position mein \u2014 face-to-face ya spooned. Wave crown se shuru hoti hai: shoulders pehle forward roll karenge, phir chest press, stomach slide, hips lift, thighs tensing, calves flexing, toes curling. Phir wave reverse hogi: toes pehle uncurl honge, calves relax, thighs soften, hips settle, stomach release, chest ease, shoulders drop. Har full pass liquid heat ki tarah feel hoga jo body chain mein travel karega \u2014 skin sequence mein garam hogi, tremors ripples ki tarah follow karenge. Sweat contact line par jama hoga, wave ko smooth current bana dega. Saansein rhythm se match hongi aur dil slow heavy sync mein dhadkenge.")
